Q: How to move message from one partition to another?
A: mboxutil -r user/test1/INBOX user/test1/INBOX second

Q: How to create another partition/s?
A: mkdir /var/opt/sun/comms/messaging64/store/partition/second
   configutil -o store.partition.second.path -v /var/opt/sun/comms/messaging64/store/partition/second/
   chown <mailuser>:<mailgrp> /var/opt/sun/comms/messaging64/store/partition/second

Q: How to create and use store expire rules?
A: Create a file /opt/sun/comms/messaging64/config/store.expirerules, refresh and run sbin/imexpire -d

Q: to run imexpire for a particular user?
A: ./imexpire -du <username>

Q: To know a user's quota?
A: /opt/sun/comms/messaging/sbin/imcheck -m user/green14/INBOX|grep Quota
